name: Chaotic Elements
desc: Add 1 Level 5 or higher LIGHT or DARK Pyro or Aqua monster from your Deck or GY to your hand, then if you have 3 or more Pyro and/or Aqua monsters in your GY, you can destroy 1 card on the field. If your opponent controls a LIGHT or DARK Pyro or Aqua monster: You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 monster your opponent controls; take control of it until the End Phase. You can only use each effect of "Chaotic Elements" once per turn.
